    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Grouping consisting of about 4,700 living species in 20 orders, characterized by the fetus being nourished during gestation by a placenta.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
